    <div class="main review-item" id="7596507">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7596507/" class="title-link">此史有关风与月</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7596507"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/54238983/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54238983/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">龙辰</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-09-11"
      class="main-meta">2015-09-11 10:21:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7596507_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      《此史有关风与月》，张明扬著，山西人民出版社，2015年6月第1版。也就算得上读史杂记与读后感吧。虽然书读得不少，但观点鲜有独到的，在历史票友中也未见得很高。也许因为媒体人的原因，出书较为容易吧。现在看历史，觉得若无一点考证而纯议论，意思不大，功力亦不深。从...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7596507_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7596507_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










